            "read_more": true,
            "icon_description": "",
            "description_expanded": true,
            "title_1": "Benefits",
            "icon_name_1": "",
            "raw_content_1": "<ul><li><strong>Absorbs instantly, no residue:</strong> Sinks in within seconds — no grease, no shine, no heavy after-feel. 100% of study participants agreed it didn’t feel greasy or sticky.</li><li><strong>Hydration that actually lasts:</strong> Japanese botanicals — rice ferment, squalane, hyaluronic acid — keep skin plump and soft hours after application, not just right away.</li><li><strong>Rebuilds your barrier with daily use:</strong> Strengthens your skin’s defenses so dryness, flaking, and sensitivity gradually decrease over time.</li><li><strong>Safe for face and body:</strong> Formulated to facial-grade standards — use everywhere including under eyes, on dry patches, and under SPF without pilling or clogging pores.</li><li><strong>Clean formula:</strong> Fragrance-free, vegan, cruelty-free — silicone-free and made without pore-clogging ingredients.</li></ul>",
            "title_2": "Key Ingredients",
            "icon_name_2": "",
            "raw_content_2": "<p>Japanese botanicals meet modern hydration science.</p><ul><li><strong>Rice Ferment Filtrate:</strong> Improves texture and elasticity with skin-smoothing amino acids.</li><li><strong>Ume Plum Extract:</strong> Brightens skin tone and protects against glycation-induced aging.</li><li><strong>Squalane + Hemisqualane:</strong> Skin-mimicking emollients that hydrate without clogging pores.</li><li><strong>Sodium Hyaluronate</strong>: Draws water deep into skin for long-lasting plumpness.</li><li><strong>Rice Bran Extract:</strong> Antioxidant-rich and packed with vitamins to defend and soften.</li><li><strong>Arginine:</strong> An essential amino acid that supports hydration and barrier repair.</li></ul><p>Full ingredients: Water, Propanediol, C15-19 Alkane, Caprylic/Capric Triglyceride, Glyceryl Stearate, Squalane, Rosa Damascena Flower Water, Stearic Acid, Glycerin, Leuconostoc/Rice Ferment Filtrate Extract, Prunus Mume Fruit Extract, Sodium Hyaluronate, Dipotassium Glycyrrhizate, Oryza Sativa (Rice) Bran Extract, Arginine, Hydroxypropylmethylcellulose Stearoxy Ether, Behenyl Alcohol, Polyglyceryl-10 Stearate, Ethylhexylglycerin, Phenoxyethanol.</p>",
            "title_3": "How to Use",
            "icon_name_3": "",
            "raw_content_3": "<p><strong>Morning Ritual:</strong></p><p><strong>Cleanse</strong>: Apply Skin Wash to wet hands and massage onto damp face and body. Rinse thoroughly.</p><p><strong>Hydrate</strong>: Apply Skin Emulsion to face and body while skin is still slightly damp for optimal absorption. Layer as needed for extra cushion around eye area or dry patches. </p><p><strong>Evening Ritual:</strong></p><p><strong>Cleanse</strong>: Use Skin Wash to remove makeup, SPF, and daily impurities.</p><p><strong>Hydrate</strong>: Apply a generous layer of Skin Emulsion to your face and body as the final step to seal in moisture and support overnight repair. Layer as needed for additional hydration. </p>",
            "title_4": "",
            "icon_name_4": "",
            "raw_content_4": "",
            "title_5": "",
            "icon_name_5": "",
            "raw_content_5": "",
            "padding_bottom": 20
