    "section_faq_DJnzd7": {
      "type": "section-faq",
      "blocks": {
        "text_jQpt3T": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Can I really use it on my face and body?",
            "content": "<p>Yes. Skin Emulsion is formulated to facial-grade standards, the same quality and ingredients you'd find in premium face care. We formulate and produce in Japan using advanced emulsion technology, with ingredients like squalane, hyaluronic acid, and rice ferment. If it's good enough for your face, it's incredible everywhere else.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_bBNczc": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What is the texture like?",
            "content": "<p>It's lightweight and oil-free, designed to absorb quickly without any greasy after-feel. In our consumer study, 100% of participants agreed it didn't feel greasy or sticky. It's rich enough to hydrate deeply but never heavy.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_RY9JHL": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What does it smell like?",
            "content": "<p>Skin Emulsion is fragrance-free, but we use rose water for its hydrating benefits, which imparts a pleasant, mild scent. It's subtle and natural, not perfumed or overpowering.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_yY3XL9": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Is it safe for sensitive skin, pregnancy, and kids?",
            "content": "<p>Yes. Skin Emulsion is dermatologist-tested and clinically proven safe for sensitive skin. It's safe for use during pregnancy and nursing, and gentle enough for kids. It's also fragrance-free, vegan, and formulated to EU clean standards.</p><p>As with any new product during pregnancy or for young children, we recommend checking with your doctor or pediatrician.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
